OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry
OL,6,Fovernight with variable amounts of
OL,7,Fcloud and lengthy clear spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping with a risk of a rural
OL,9,Ffrost in the east. Turning cloudier
OL,10,Facross North Wales towards dawn.
OL,11,FMostly light winds, but breezier near
OL,12,FIrish Sea coasts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FCloudy with patchy rain
OL,15,Farriving across Wales during the
OL,16,Fmorning. Turning drier and brighter
OL,17,Finto the afternoon with sunny spells
OL,18,Fdeveloping. Perhaps the odd isolated
OL,19,Fshower in the north later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
